posts.body: The Download All button doesn't work for me anymore. The Seed button is fine, though

posts.body: Don't think this has been posted here before

>>68bfb5a1-0489-4ec8-8f35-e0fd6c3cdf90

It's because there are no seeders. I uploaded another version further down

>>b713174a-e75c-453c-87fd-6f264f60473c

Short answer: no.

I don't think I can reorder the board, but even if I could I'm not 100% of the actual order of release.

>>cf6956ee-2ec8-47c6-842c-073826c0c3dd

Pretty much. You can click the arrow on the first post and select Seed All to save you clicking on each picture, though
There's a higher quality version of this set already posted below

>>3fd6e67d-e16f-436d-8cd1-1524d53b058d

You need to seed all the files first. Any of the images with [Seed] next to them won't be zipped.
